":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e056f068e892e9f4e47077169efd9e90c0d6032","tid":2442444,"uid":350584,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"徐德義：專家商討是否可發放仔細接種指引　適時會公布"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"而家先出指引，之前啲人命點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"與疫苗沒有直接因果關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"接種疫苗純粹個人意願，當時人有評估當中風險才作出決定，作為成年人，理應為自己決定負上責任，不應歸咎於政府。<br />\n新指引並不代表以前資訊有誤導成份，新指引是一個補充資料。新指引提供市民更清晰資訊作參考，釋除公眾疑慮，相信日後會有更多人接種疫苗。"},{"pid":"7a35de0a9ad057bd88e30280cbe8682ec2267655","tid":2442444,"uid":1108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"源頭減廢針<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達爾文針<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cd2269a229b42a0cf4c2d5192b81f8da0c819a","tid":2442444,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c6a62f882c1329c93654704bc69cb908911b9d6","tid":2442444,"uid":57269,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"82121eb00ecbe867e3988b161cacdc2c73e9166e","tid":2442444,"uid":350584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"34c31ca8a4adf110671d0baf7c8a25de729d215f","tid":2442444,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"而家先出指引，之前啲人命點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"與疫苗沒有直接因果關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"接種疫苗純粹個人意願，當時人有評估當中風險才作出決定，作為成年人，理應為自己決定負上責任，不應歸咎於政府。<br />\n新指引並不代表以前資訊有誤導成份，新指引是一個補充資料。新指引提供市民更清晰資訊作參考，釋除公眾疑慮，相信日後會有更多人接種疫苗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr